text: Tibor Foco (born 18 April 1956, Linz, Austria) is the killer of Elfriede Hochgatterer (13 March 1986). He escaped from the Linz prison in 1995. His place of residence is unknown. == References == == Other websites == *Europol: Europe's most wanted fugitives *Interpol Category:Murder in Austria Category:Murder in the 1980s
